name: Russian Attack

name: Russian Attack
column4: The occupiers tried to dislodge our troops from the Dementiivka district. But our soldiers successfully repelled several assaults on the mentioned village and forced the enemy to retreat.

description: Russians are trying to push in the direction of Svitlychne (1)
column4: but they are getting hammered by Ukrainian artillery along the way. They are also trying to dislodge Ukraine from Dementiivka (2) but their attacks are routinely repelled.
